    {
      "text": "Bonanza Bros. (sometimes written Bonanza Brothers) is a 3D-style, 2D side-scrolling stealth action game developed and released by Sega in 1990. It is one of the earliest arcade games powered by the Sega System 24 arcade system board. It was ported to various home systems, including the Mega Drive/Genesis, Master System, PC-Engine/TurboGrafx-CD, and several home computers.\nBonanza Bros. received praise for its graphics, soundtrack, and character dialogue. It has been remastered and rereleased several times.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
